thread.title: Soap | EastEnders

author: Sheena McGinley
title: Soap | EastEnders
text: As the fallout from the events at court continues, Carol admits to Sonia she is fed up of her daily routine - although she does eventually realise she has a way out, if she is willing to take it. Helllew Robbie! However, things are interrupted by Lauren, who needs help persuading Abi to move out of the Mitchells'. Meanwhile, Mick tells Linda about Lee's depression, only for his son to overhear the conversation and insist that everything is fine. Can his mum get him to open up about his feelings?
